00036       FirstInPairFind(const char* x) { m_x = x; };
00037       bool operator()( pair<const char*, const char*> y) const {
00038          return StringUtility::strcmp(m_x, y.first) == 0;

00257       void addTmpZipCode(const char* zipCode, const char* zipArea) {
00258          MC2_ASSERT(zipCode != NULL);
00259          vector< pair<const char*, const char*> >::const_iterator it = 
00260              find_if(m_zips.begin(), m_zips.end(), FirstInPairFind(zipCode));
00261          if (it == m_zips.end()) {
00262             const char* zc = StringUtility::newStrDup(zipCode);
00263             const char* za = NULL;
00264             if (zipArea != NULL)
00265                za = StringUtility::newStrDup(zipArea);
00266             m_zips.push_back(make_pair(zc, za));
00267          }
00268       }
00269 
00270       uint32 getNbrTmpZipCodes() {
00271          return m_zips.size();
00272       }
00273 
00274       const char* getTmpZipCode(uint32 zipNbr) {
00275          MC2_ASSERT(zipNbr < m_zips.size());
00276          return m_zips[zipNbr].first;
00277       }
